Third-party licenses
====================

Kovault backend ships the following third-party Python packages inside the
kovault-mcp Docker image. Each is distributed under its own license, reproduced/obtainable at
the upstream links below.

- fastmcp — Apache-2.0 — MCP server framework.
  https://github.com/jlowin/fastmcp

- psycopg (psycopg3) — LGPL-3.0-only — PostgreSQL database adapter.
  https://github.com/psycopg/psycopg

- httpx — BSD-3-Clause — HTTP client used for the embedding endpoint.
  https://github.com/encode/httpx

Not redistributed (pulled by the operator at deploy time, not bundled in this repo's images):
the ParadeDB/PostgreSQL image, Ollama, and any embedding model (e.g. Qwen3-Embedding). These
carry their own licenses from their respective upstreams.
